o-blog/creating-an-effective-digital-marketing\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"w-full\\\",\\\"aria-label\\\":\\\"Developing Piano Technique: From Beginner to Advanced Mastery\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"figure\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"overflow-hidden\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L10\\\",null,{\\\"src\\\":\\\"/images/blog-img/blog-img-6.png\\\",\\\"width\\\":355,\\\"height\\\":345,\\\"alt\\\":\\\"Developing Piano Technique: From Beginner to Advanced Mastery\\\",\\\"className\\\":\\\"h-full w-full transition-all duration-500 hover:scale-125\\\"}]}],[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"rv-badge mt-6 md:mt-7\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"span\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"rv-badge-text\\\",\\\"children\\\":\\\"$undefined\\\"}]}],\\\"$L23\\\",\\\"$L24\\\"]}]}],\\\"$L25\\\",\\\"$L26\\\"]}]]}]}]}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"19:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"section\\\",null,{\\\"id\\\":\\\"faq\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L27\\\",null,{\\\"data\\\":{\\\"italicTitle\\\":\\\"Frequently\\\",\\\"headingTitle\\\":\\\"Asked Questions\\\",\\\"description\\\":\\\"Common questions about piano lessons, music composition, and performance opportunities with Metta Legita.\\\",\\\"faqs\\\":[{\\\"id\\\":1,\\\"question\\\":\\\"What ages and skill levels do you teach?\\\",\\\"answer\\\":\\\"I teach students of all ages, from children as young as 6 years old to adults. Whether you're a complete beginner or an advanced player looking to refine your technique, I can tailor lessons to your needs and goals.\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":2,\\\"question\\\":\\\"Do you teach both classical and contemporary/jazz styles?\\\",\\\"answer\\\":\\\"Yes! I specialize in both classical piano technique and contemporary/jazz styles. My background includes classical training with jazz and contemporary influences, allowing me to teach a comprehensive approach to piano playing.\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":3,\\\"question\\\":\\\"How long are your piano lessons and what's the frequency?\\\",\\\"answer\\\":\\\"Lessons are typically 45-60 minutes long. For best results, I recommend weekly lessons, but we can adjust the schedule based on your availability and learning pace. Consistency is key to musical development.\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":4,\\\"question\\\":\\\"Do you accept performance bookings?\\\",\\\"answer\\\":\\\"Yes, I accept bookings for solo piano performances, jazz trio/quartet engagements, and orchestral collaborations. Please contact me well in advance for availability, repertoire planning, and venue requirements.\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":5,\\\"question\\\":\\\"Can you compose custom music for films, events, or personal projects?\\\",\\\"answer\\\":\\\"Absolutely! I compose original works for film scoring, corporate events, weddings, and personal projects. My style blends contemporary and orchestral elements. Let's discuss your vision and create something unique.\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":6,\\\"question\\\":\\\"Do you offer online lessons for international students?\\\",\\\"answer\\\":\\\"Yes, I provide online piano lessons via video conferencing. This works well for students who prefer remote learning or are located outside Phnom Penh. The online format is interactive and effective for skill development.\\\"}]}}]}]\\n\"])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1a:[\\\"$\\\",\\\"section\\\",null,{\\\"id\\\":\\\"cta\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"section\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"relative pb-[70px] pt-14 md:pt-16 lg:pb-[140px] lg:pt-[88px] xl:pt-[100px]\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"div\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"container\\\",\\\"children\\\":[[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$La\\\",null,{\\\"children\\\":[\\\"$\\\",\\\"h2\\\",null,{\\\"className\\\":\\\"text-center font-normal xl:text-[96px] xl:leading-[1.1] xl:tracking-[-2.88px]\\\",\\\"children\\\":[\\\"Let's create\\\",[\\\"$\\\",\\\"$L28\\\",null,{\\\"slides\\\":[{\\\"id\\\":\\\"1\\\",\\\"img\\\":\\\"/images/agent/01.jpg\\\"},{\\\"id\\\":\\\"2\\\",\\\"img\\\":\\\"/images/agent/02.jpg\\\"},{\\\"id\\\